<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hwdẖạ ạlḥbyb wạfy̱</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hūadẖā ạl̊ḥabību wāfay̱
 ẓāhiraⁿạ baẙna ạlạảnām̊
 yaj̊dẖibu ạl̊qal̊ba ạn̊ʿiṭāfā
 biạl̊wadādi wālsãlạm̊

[V2]
 2- hūadẖā ạl̊kẖub̊zu ạlsãmāwī̃̊
 qad̊ ạảtānā min̊ ʿulạh̊
 ại̹nãhu kẖaẙru ṭaʿāmiⁿ
 ạảk̊luhu yuʿ̊ṭī ạl̊ḥayāh̊

[V3]
 3- hūadẖā sẖakẖ̊ṣu ạl̊ḥabībi
 ʿalay̱ ạl̊bābi yaq̊raʿu
 fah̊wa ʿizĩy wanaṣībī
 waṣaẘtahu ạảs̊maʿu

[V4]
 4- hakadẖā yad̊kẖulu qal̊bī
 wayataʿasẖãy̱ maʿī
 ại̹nãhu yasūʿu rabĩy
 dẖātahu yuẓ̊hiru lī</lyrics>
</song>